{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_05_05",
  "title": "LizNoir 05 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、まず軽く十キロ走って体を温めましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ first let's warm up with a light 10km run.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.9434467475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "じゅっ、十キロ！？　しかもそれで軽く！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-ten kilometers!? And you call that light!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9434467475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに走ったら、脚が太くなっちゃいます～\nこころはアイドルとして、それはどうかと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My legs will get too thick if I run that much~\nI think that's a bit much for me as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫。僕は毎日二十キロ走ってるけど太くないよ\nむしろ細いくらいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine. I run 20km every day and my legs aren't thick.\nIn fact‚ they're pretty thin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.11,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "葵は体脂肪率十五パーセント台だものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi's body fat percentage is in the 15% range‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "それって一流アスリート並みなんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's like…top athlete level…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "一流のダンサーだって、そんなものよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's normal for a top dancer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.2666666684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "先輩方はダンス中毒だから、そんなこと言えるんです\n私達はあくまでも可憐なアイドルですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You guys can say that because you're dance addicts.\nWe're supposed to be dainty idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.61,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことするのは、アホくさいなんて\n愛ちゃんしか言ってません～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan's the only one who said it was stupid\nto do something like that~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "言ってません！　言ってません！\nこころは、また私のせいにして～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't say it! I didn't!\nKokoro‚ you're blaming me again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2533333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "前回の復活ライブの動画を莉央とチェックしたんだ\n結論として、君達はやっぱりスキル不足だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio and I reviewed the video of your last comeback live.\nOur conclusion is that you two are still lacking in skill.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕と莉央が前に出て、君達はバックだから\n目立ってないけど、それでも合格点はあげられない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were in the front and you two were in the back‚ so\nyou weren't as noticeable‚ but we still can't give you a passing grade.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、特に後半は酷かったわ\n二人とも足がフラついてたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ the second half was especially bad.\nYou were both stumbling‚ weren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けを手順通りにこなすので精一杯って感じよ\nそれはダンスとは言えないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It felt like you were just barely managing to get through the choreography.\nThat's not dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes‚ I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "こころは愛嬌を振りまくのに必死なので\nあえて体力を温存してまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so busy being charming\nthat I purposely conserved my energy~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスと歌は先輩方と愛ちゃんに譲ってさし上げる\nということで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll leave the dancing and singing to you guys and Ai-chan.\nTherefore――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "……さあ、はりきって走りますよ\n愛ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ let's get running‚\nAi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7566666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、待ってよ、こころ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ wait for me‚ Kokoro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "五分経ったら、私達もスタートするわ\n私達に抜かれたら、十キロ追加よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll start in five minutes.\nIf we overtake you‚ it's another 10km.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ひい～～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeeeek…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 107.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ\n走らせるだけでも、一苦労だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good grief.\nGetting them to run is a struggle in itself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……あの二人にあって、私達にないものって何かしら\n全然分からないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do those two have that we don't?\nI have no idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕はそんなもの最初からないと思うな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think there was anything like that in the first place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333334000004,
          "startTime": 123.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
